description:
“What I Like About You” by The Romantics 60's Soul style cover by Postmodern Jukebox ft. Tia Simone.
Get The Song: http://pmjlive.com/rizz | Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPMJ | World Tour Tix: http://pmjtour.com
